OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FEarly low cloud and mist
OL,6,Fburning back to North Sea coasts
OL,7,Fduring the morning where it may
OL,8,Flinger. Very warm or hot again inland,
OL,9,Fbut cooler and fresher around the east
OL,10,Fcoast.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FThe low cloud around the
OL,13,FNorth Sea coast moving inland. Staying
OL,14,Fdry with mainly clear skies through
OL,15,FDumfries and Galloway. Winds remaining
OL,16,Flight.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
