OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CFriday:FAny low cloud should clear
OL,6,Fduring the morning with bright and
OL,7,Fsunny spells. Temperatures down a bit,
OL,8,Fbut still warm or very warm in any
OL,9,Fsunshine. Light northerly winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FMainly
OL,12,Fdry and settled with bright and sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Temperatures around normal,
OL,14,Ffeeling warm or very warm in the
OL,15,Fsunshine. Some cloudier periods
OL,16,Fexpected.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
